overview: Collection of live material 2002-2003. DVD 1 Tracks 1-20: Live at Melkweg Netherlands 2002. Tracks 21-26: With Full Force 2003. DVD 2 Live at the Hultsfred Festival 2003. Also contains the features (Surprise Section - Vault From The Past):  *On Japanese TV *Buffalo - NY (bootleg quality) *Interview at With Full Force Festival *Board Stage  Screen 4:3 PAL/NTSC Sound: PCM Stereo Country Code: All Regions Duration: Appr. 4 hrs
